                    color: '#64748b',
                    maxWidth: '700px',
                    margin: '0 auto 40px',
                    lineHeight: '1.8'
                }}>
                    Each AI agent is a specialized tool built for automotive excellence.
                    Activate them individually, or combine them all to unlock the full power of Genius.
                </p>

                {/* Progress Bar */}
                <div style={{
                    maxWidth: '600px',
                    margin: '40px auto',
                    background: '#1e293b',
                    borderRadius: '20px',
                    padding: '8px',
                    border: '2px solid #334155'
                }}>
                    <div style={{
                        height: '12px',
                        background: allActive
                            ? 'linear-gradient(90deg, #fbbf24, #f59e0b)'
                            : 'linear-gradient(90deg, #8B5CF6, #14B8A6)',
                        borderRadius: '12px',
                        width: `${progressPercent}%`,
                        transition: 'all 0.5s ease',
                        boxShadow: allActive ? '0 0 20px #fbbf24' : '0 0 20px #8B5CF6'
